  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    app_utils
    Static methods for Carlsbad applications: threads, results display.
    carlsbad_utils
    Static utility methods for CARLSBAD database system.
    carlsbadone_app
    CARLSBAD "one-click" subnet query app.
    carlsbadone_servlet
    CarlsbadOne, a one-step, bioactivity data-mining, evidence-driven application for biophamaceutical knowledge discovery via cheminformatics, chemogenomics and systems pharmaco-informatics.
    carlsbadone_utils
    Static methods for CARLSBAD "one-click" subnet queries.
    CCP
    Provides fast in-memory CCP (Common Chemical Pattern) data storage; used by CCPList.
    CCPList
    Maps CCPs to CIDs, TIDs.
    Compound
    Provides fast in-memory compound data storage; used by CompoundList.
    Compound2Network_Task
    CARLSBAD "one-click" subnet extraction via threaded Callable task.
    CompoundList
    Maps CIDs to Compounds, and compound names to CIDs.
    cytoscapeview_servlet
    CytoscapeWeb container for Carlsbad.
    Disease
    Provides fast in-memory drug (compound) data storage; used by DiseaseList.
    Disease2Network_Task
    CARLSBAD "one-click" subnet extraction via threaded Callable task.
    DiseaseList
    Handles KEGG disease list, names and KIDs.
    DiseaseList_kegg
    Handles KEGG disease list, names and KIDs.
    Drug
    Provides fast in-memory drug (compound) data storage; used by DrugList.
    Extract2XGMML_Task
    CARLSBAD subnet extraction via threaded Callable task.
    snake_app
    Utility SNAKE command-line app for CARLSBAD database system.
    snake_servlet
    Uses PostgreSQL JDBC & chemical cartrige gNova Chord DB.
    Target
    Provides fast in-memory target data storage; used by TargetList.
    Target2Network_Task
    CARLSBAD "one-click" subnet extraction via threaded Callable task.
    TargetList
    Maps target TIDs to Targets with names, etc., and names to TIDs.
